{"tid":1472371,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Hkprotect 暫停營業","createTime":"2019-08-14T14:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T06:42:26.000Z","uid":44559,"like":98,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"a64944426c7de4ebc63ef4e10cfd7a161c334751","tid":1472371,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:21:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkprotect.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkprotect.org%2F&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXJmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=024f90ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkprotect.org/</a><br />\n<br />\n14/8/2019 公告<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n本店暫停營業直至另行通知。<br />\n12/8/2019 緊急公告 &ndash; 跪求支持<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n本周未我地有手足俾強力部門捉到，被充公左三十多萬元既貨。本店將重組人手、搬倉庫到新的地址、及暫停所有從中國入貨的渠道。海外來貨渠道不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n現時本店將暫停接收所有新訂單。舊訂單將排隊寄出，由於現時只有海外進貨渠道通行，客人收貨時間會由現時約兩星期增加至一個月以上。<br />\n<br />\n如客戶需要退款請inbox/ email 我們。<br />\n<br />\n因重組事忙，現時未必能逐一回覆留言，請留言後耐心等待。<br />\n<br />\n請對我們有信心，我們將於一個月內重組完成，繼續為大家提供成本價之貨品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知重會唔會送貨/退錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9550052fe113fc00bb09bb4bbcb533e86e50bc5d","tid":1472371,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8215579173c60a894f209992e354130c2c7b6030","tid":1472371,"uid":268213,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/adJu4RB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FadJu4RB.jpg&h=8903454d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hVwP4RB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhVwP4RB.jpg&h=3d3df616&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"454ee4ad596d52671aa865e28cd134a5fb713b3b","tid":1472371,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:50:30.000Z","msg":"0818 維園"},{"pid":"184cc16d60c5331a49